title: Can Sabalenka beat Kyrgios and what if she loses? The key questions in 'Battle of the Sexes'
subtitle: BBC Sport looks at the key questions going into the divisive Battle of the Sexes-style match between Aryna Sabalenka and Nick Kyrgios on Sunday.
